Here are the steps I followed. However, you could download the project folder(my-app) with all the files and skip Step 3  

Step 1-> Download Node.js: 
https://nodejs.org/en/

Step 2->Install create react app: 
npm install -g create-react-app

Step 3->Inside your desired directory create a project(my-app): 
create-react-app my-app

Step 4->Navigate inside my-app folder using : 
cd my-app

Step 5->Then run: 
npm start  

Step 6->React-MDL: 
npm install --save react-mdl 

Step 7->Router dom:
npm add react-router-dom

